{"tid":1492443,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我發咗兩個夢","createTime":"2019-08-21T00:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T02:55:30.000Z","uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fef37280c6f2e1a3b1105914d121b8a19d921ab9","tid":1492443,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T00:01:33.000Z","msg":"1. 防攻之後齊糕糕突然間有車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟手一嘢膊咗就繼續膊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後無啦啦頭頭就sacked<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就順手腰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 呢個唔太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到2000個梨..有雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要有貼相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街好撚真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但諗落好似兩個連到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁樣咪仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好囉囉！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743496d15100915663fb5c97d6398ac13f9958b0","tid":1492443,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T00:13:17.000Z","msg":"係真"},{"